OL,3,CFirst man jailed for stirring up
OL,4,Cracial hatred online during riots
OL,6,FA man has become the first to be
OL,7,Fjailed for stirring up racial hatred
OL,8,Fonline during the recent riots.
OL,10,FJordan Parlour, 28, posted comments on
OL,11,FFacebook advocating an attack on a
OL,12,Fhotel in Leeds where around 200 asylum
OL,13,Fseekers were housed.
OL,15,FThe comments were reported to West
OL,16,FYorkshire Police and Parlour was
OL,17,Fsubsequently arrested by officers.
