OL,4,Cracial hatred online during riots
OL,6,FThe hotel manager put the building
OL,7,Finto lockdown on Saturday, 3 August
OL,8,Fdue to the disorder in Leeds, and at
OL,9,Fleast one window was broken after
OL,10,Fstones were thrown over the weekend.
OL,12,FThe court heard Parlour posted the
OL,13,Fcomments after the hotel had been
OL,14,Ftargeted with people throwing missiles
OL,15,Fand breaking windows, and more attacks
OL,16,Fhappened later.
OL,18,FThe post was before a hotel housing
OL,19,Fasylum seekers in Rotherham was
OL,20,Fattacked, the court was told.
