OL,4,Cracial hatred online during riots
OL,6,FThere was no evidence that Parlour
OL,7,Fattended the hotel, but the Recorder
OL,8,Fof Leeds, Judge Guy Kearl KC, said:
OL,9,F"There can be no doubt you were
OL,10,Finciting others to do so, otherwise
OL,11,Fwhy post the comments?"
OL,13,FNicholas Hammond, defending, told the
OL,14,Fjudge his client was "not part of any
OL,15,Fsinister group activity designed to
OL,16,Fstir up violence" and was "not
OL,17,Faffiliated with any group".
