OL,4,Cracial hatred online during riots
OL,6,FRosemary Ainslie, Acting Head of the
OL,7,FCPS Special Crime and Counter
OL,8,FTerrorism Division, said: "Let me be
OL,9,Fabsolutely clear, people who think
OL,10,Fthey can hide behind their keyboards
OL,11,Fand stir up racial hatred should think
OL,12,Fagain.
OL,14,F"Jordan Parlour advocated violence
OL,15,Fthrough his online posts and risked
OL,16,Fthe safety of those staying and
OL,17,Fworking at the hotel.
