OL,6,F"He is now facing a prison sentence
OL,7,Ffor his actions, and I hope this
OL,8,Fserves as a stark reminder that online
OL,9,Factions have consequences.
OL,11,F"The CPS will continue to act swiftly
OL,12,Fand robustly regarding these cases and
OL,13,Fensure those responsible for such
OL,14,Fdeplorable criminality are brought to
OL,15,Fjustice."
